    = \frac{\hbar}{2(2\pi)^D}\mbox{Tr}\int dX\int d^Dp\,\,\,G_0(p)
    \\ \\
        {\cal L}^{(1)}_1
    = \frac{\hbar}{2(2\pi)^D}\mbox{Tr}\int dX
    \int d^Dp\,\,\,G_0(p)\Delta_1(p)G_0(p)
