    \int d^Dp\,\,\,G_0(p)\Delta_1(p)G_0(p)\Delta_1(p)G_0(p)\;\\ \vdots \\ \mbox{etc.}
  \end{array}
\end{eqnarray}
and Tr denotes a trace over gauge indices (including possibly spinor indices).
In this work, we will be working up to ${\cal L}^{(1)}_4$.

