\subsection{${\cal L}^{(1)}_0$: $0$th-order Mass-Dimensional Lagrangians}
After having gathered the terms of interest that resulted in the Taylor series expansion, we now group the terms into their common mass-dimensions (as indicated in their names and the numbers inside the $[\,]$ notation).

%\vspace{0.3cm}
\begin{large}
