   \mbox{Tr}
\left(
   {\cal {\cal X}}-{\cal {\cal X}}_0
\right)
\end{eqnarray}
The terms contained here are contributed from (\ref{a2}) and (\ref{h2}), respectively. Eqn. (\ref{0[2]}) is exactly Eqn. (2.71) of \cite{Rodf-Diss}.
